[MUSIC]

00:08:11.230 --> 00:08:16.701
The race is sponsored by DARPA, Defense
Advance Research Projects Agency.

00:08:17.740 --> 00:08:21.480
Their goal is to stimulate technology
that can be used by the military.

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:27.620
&gt;&gt; If we can use unmanned vehicles in
dangerous missions like living supplies

00:08:27.620 --> 00:08:28.959
