she was a driver of a supply vehicle and

00:08:38.460 --> 00:08:42.710
if that was an autonomous vehicle,
that episode would have never happened.

00:08:42.710 --> 00:08:44.810
True autonomy, that's what we're after.

00:08:44.809 --> 00:08:46.858
It's a hard problem.

00:08:49.019 --> 00:08:53.210
&gt;&gt; Just how hard a problem it is to
create a vehicle that can drive itself

00:08:53.210 --> 00:08:57.550
became painfully clear a year earlier
at the first Grand Challenge race.

00:08:58.960 --> 00:09:04.184
Carnegie Mellon was one of 15
teams at the starting line.

00:09:06.600 --> 00:09:11.430
Racing against the clock, Sandstorm
was the first robot out of the game.

00:09:11.429 --> 00:09:16.639
To win, it had to run a course across
142 miles of ragged desert terrain

00:09:16.639 --> 00:09:17.588
in less than ten hours.

00:09:21.779 --> 00:09:24.430
But just seven miles from the start,

00:09:24.431 --> 00:09:28.288
Sandstorm drifted off course and
got stuck on a rock.

00:09:28.288 --> 00:09:31.872
In a valiant effort to keep moving,

00:09:31.873 --> 00:09:38.140
the robot spun its wheels until
its tires burst into flame.

00:09:38.139 --> 00:09:41.539
Back at the start, other robots
were having their own problems.

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:49.615
&gt;&gt; Everything was set up for this high
speed rumble of all these vehicles.

00:09:49.615 --> 00:09:55.634
This careening through the dessert and
that's not how it happened.

00:09:55.634 --> 00:10:01.680
&gt;&gt; All 15 robots died of mechanical
failure, half in the first mile.

00:10:01.679 --> 00:10:05.589
In this group of losers,
Sandstorm went the farthest,

00:10:05.590 --> 00:10:09.280
leaving many to believe no robot
could ever win the grand challenge.

00:10:10.440 --> 00:10:13.630
&gt;&gt; The fact that the vehicle's
only traveled a short distance

00:10:13.629 --> 00:10:15.259
show's that it was a tough
technical problem.

00:10:15.259 --> 00:10:19.518
But where the success really lies in the
amount of people that actually responded

00:10:19.518 --> 00:10:20.524
to the challenge.

00:10:20.524 --> 00:10:23.889
[MUSIC]

