Red gets excited about seeing his robots
do powerful things in the real world

00:12:13.269 --> 00:12:15.250
&gt;&gt; Think it's going to work.

00:12:15.250 --> 00:12:18.649
&gt;&gt; The thing, at this stage of the game,
it's making it work, right?

00:12:18.649 --> 00:12:20.039
Making it work.

00:12:20.039 --> 00:12:23.206
&gt;&gt; Take the hood off.

00:12:23.206 --> 00:12:31.232
[MUSIC]

00:12:31.232 --> 00:12:33.768
&gt;&gt; The red team will spend
several months replacing and

00:12:33.769 --> 00:12:35.620
modifying Highlander's hardware.

00:12:38.129 --> 00:12:42.274
&gt;&gt; A tremendous amount
of these desert raising

00:12:42.274 --> 00:12:46.197
machines is heavy metal
iron [INAUDIBLE].

00:12:46.197 --> 00:12:50.190
It's heating and beating and
bashing and cutting and making.

00:12:51.519 --> 00:12:54.460
It's as important as
any of the software.

00:12:54.460 --> 00:12:55.059
It's a lot of fun.

